      • addCloseCallback

        default void addCloseCallback​(InternalTransaction.TransactionClosedCallback callback)
        Attach a callback that will be called when the transaction is closed. This can be used by e.g. procedures to register resources that should be closed together with the transaction.
        Parameters:
        callback - to be invoked when the transaction is closed.
